          <declname>out_snapshot</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Pulls in the state of all persistent transforms and all enabled trackers extrapolated to the provided timestamp. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This timestamp typically comes from out_frame_info.predicted_display_time out parameter from the MLGraphicsBeginFrameEx function.</para>
<para>Returns a <ref refid="group___perception_1gaa14a3ce2de93527687c615433aad4d23" kindref="member">MLSnapshot</ref> with this latest state. This snap should be used for the duration of the frame being constructed and then released with a call to <computeroutput><ref refid="group___perception_1ga9ecc623e84bd956436108024a0ad68bb" kindref="member">MLPerceptionReleaseSnapshot()</ref></computeroutput>.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>API Level:\n 27</title><para></para>
</simplesect>
<parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">timestamp</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Timestamp representing the time for which to predict poses. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">out_snapshot</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to a pointer containing an <ref refid="group___perception_1gaa14a3ce2de93527687c615433aad4d23" kindref="member">MLSnapshot</ref> on success.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<parameterlist kind="retval"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>MLResult_Ok</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Successfully created snapshot. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>MLResult_InvalidTimestamp</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Timestamp is either more than 100ms in the future or too old for cached state. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>MLResult_InvalidParam</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Output parameter was not valid (null). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>MLResult_PerceptionSystemNotStarted</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Perception System has not been started.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<xrefsect id="permissions_1_permissions000623"><xreftitle>Required Permissions</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>None </para>
